title.rendered: European Ecommerce Marketplaces and What to Sell in Europe with Luke Havard of Dwarfs.io

content.rendered:
Podcast: Play in new window | Download (Duration: 19:13 — 17.6MB)

Subscribe: Spotify | Email | RSS

Podcast (10k-podcast): Play in new window | Download (Duration: 19:13 — 17.6MB)

Subscribe: Spotify | Email | TuneIn | RSS

We are coming into this second part of a discussion with Luke Havard from dwarf.io. They are basically the people that specialize in European-based Ecommerce businesses. And in particular, they work with Amazon-based businesses, but also non-Amazon businesses and some of the really attractive marketplaces. Hope you enjoy the show.

 

You’ll Learn:

  • How do you pick a marketplace that is best for you?
  • The different European marketplaces similar to Amazon
  • How to build a database and webshop
  • That quite a few sellers in Europe DON’T source in China
  • What sells and doesn’t sell in Europe
